        "subject": "LU-2665 mdc: Keep resend FLocks",
        "message": "LU-2665 mdc: Keep resend FLocks\n\nFLocks requests (particulary F_UNLCKs) can't be trashed\nupon comm problems with Server/MDS nor upon kill/exit,\nthus we need to keep retry/send.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I1e2753926eb6726874135ec852a0a150d7b2e8fe\nReviewed-on: http://review.whamcloud.com/6407\nTested-by: Hudson\nTested-by: Maloo <whamcloud.maloo@gmail.com>\nReviewed-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam@gmail.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\n"
